Class GaussianPotentialField

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.leonis.algieba.spatial.GaussianPotentialField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class GaussianPotentialField
extends java.lang.Object
implements PotentialField, LocalLinearLineIntegral
    The Class GaussianPotentialField. This class represents a PotentialField of an object which is modeled after a two-dimensional normal distribution.
